Ben Webster (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ben_Webster_(actor) 0 Ben Webster (2 June 1864 – 26 February 1947) was an English-born actor, and the husband of actress Dame May Whitty, and father of the British-American stage actress Margaret Webster. Ben_Webster ( 2_June_1864 – 26_February_1947 ) was an_English-born_actor , and the_husband of actress_Dame_May_Whitty , and father of the_British-American_stage_actress_Margaret_Webster .
